title: Tea and Coffee Stain Remover
description:
Now available in Bed Bath and Beyond!
Astonish Tea and Coffee stain remover has a powerful oxy cleaning action!
Removes Tea and coffee stains!
Easy to use no scrubbing required
Taint free
Items restored to like new!
Ideal for use on china, metal, glass, plastics and flasks!
